            <div class="text-center pt24 pb24 o_colored_level col-lg-4" style="">
              <span class="s_number display-4"><img class="img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="web/image/237868-78ebdca1/telecharger-pdf.png" alt="" data-original-title="" title="" aria-describedby="tooltip404221" style="width: 25% !important;" loading="lazy" data-original-id="237843" data-original-src="/web/image/237843-78ebdca1/telecharger-pdf.png" data-mimetype="image/png" data-resize-width="176"/>​</span>
